@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eopvlb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.23) + 0.10) + 0.91)
    tmp = (0.85 / ((v2 + 0.80 * tmp + 0.20) - 0.69))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.18) / v0) * v1)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.02) / 0.99) * (wp.abs(v1 + 0.37) + 0.70))
    data[tid] = v0
